detailedDescription.articleBody: Joanne Vannicola is a Canadian actress. She is most noted for her roles as Dr. Naadiah in Being Erica on Netflix, Dr. Mia Stone in PSI Factor, Jerri in Love and Human Remains, Sam in Stonewall, and Renee in Slasher: Guilty Party, as well as voice roles in Crash Canyon and My Dad the Rock Star.
